name: Dimsum
description:
Dimsum is an image I drew around mid 2021 using Wacom Cintiq and Clip Studio Paint. I even live-streamed it on Twitch. It took several hours because I also enjoyed talking to my viewers at the same time.

Two buns you see are actually tiny creatures called sea slugs or nudibranchs. Some people call them sea bunnies as well. I really love how they look.

Hope you enjoy seeing them too.

With love ♡,

Obchoey
